      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and has been well-loved! I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
