    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_23",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically robust, the VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced, addressing the platform's primary structural concerns. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and new bushings to maintain sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. While the aesthetics reflect its status as an enjoyed performance machine, the drivetrain remains tight and the engine pulls strongly through the entire powerband.",
